Discussion.S:
Although previous reports had indicated a projection 
    from the ILC to the insular cortex (Saper, 82b; Room et al., 85), 
    we found that this is a relatively minor pathway.

References.S:
Koh (1978) Anatomical evidence of direct projections 
    from the nucleus of the solitary tract to the hypothalamus, 
    amygdala and other forebrain structures in the rat.
